GetTarget (script event)
========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Returns the requested target entity.

Usage
-----

*entity* getTarget( *float* num )

Parameters
----------

-   [num] - The target number to return.

